quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  8,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  8,1,( ae Mohammad ! Mujahid log ) tum se ghanemat ke maal ke baray mein daryaft karte hain ke (kiya hukum hai ) keh do ke ghanemat khuda aur is ke rasool ka maal hai. to khuda se daro aur aapas mein sulah rakho aur agar imaan rakhtay ho to khuda aur is ke rasool ke hukum par chalo
  8,2,momin to woh hain ke jab khuda ka zikarkiya jata hai ke un ke dil dar jatay hain aur jab inhen is ki ayatain parh kar sunai jati hain to un ka imaan aur barh jata hai. aur woh apne perwar-digaar par bharosa rakhtay hain
  8,3,( aur ) woh jo namaz parhte hain aur jo maal hum ne un ko diya hai is mein se ( naik kamon mein ) kharch karte hain
  8,4,yahi sachey momin hain aur un ke liye perwar-digaar ke haan ( barray barray darjay ) aur bakhshish aur izzat ki rozi hai
  8,5,( un logon ko apne gharon se isi terhan niklana chahiye tha ) jis terhan tumahray perwar-digaar ne tum ko tadbeer ke sath apne ghar se nikala aur ( is waqt ) mominon aik jamaat nakhush thi
  8,6,woh log haq baat mein is ke zahir hue peechay tum se jhagrnay lagey goya mout ki taraf dhkile jatay hain aur usay dekh rahay hain
  8,7,aur ( is waqt ko yaad karo ) jab khuda tum se wada karta tha ke ( abu-safyaan aur aboj_hl ke ) do garohoon mein se aik giroh tumhara ( maskhar ) hojaye ga. aur tum chahtay they ke jo qaafla be ( shaan o ) Shaukat ( yani be hathyaar hai ) woh tumahray haath aajay aur khuda chahta tha ke apne farmaan se haq ko qaim rakhay aur kafiroon ki jarr kaat kar ( pheink ) day
  8,8,taakay sach ko sach aur jhoot ko jhoot kardey. go mushriq nakhush hi hon
  8,9,jab tum apne perwar-digaar se faryaad karte they to is ne tumhari dua qubool karli ( aur farmaya ) ke ( tasalii rakho ) hum hazaar firshton se jo aik dosray ke peechay atay jayen ge tumhari madad karen ge
  8,10,aur is madad ko khuda ne mehez basharat banaya tha ke tumahray dil se itminan haasil karen. aur madad to allah hi ki taraf se hai. be shak khuda ghalib hikmat wala hai
  8,11,jab is ne ( tumhari ) taskeen ke liye apni taraf se tumhe neend ( ki chadar ) udha di aur tum par aasman se pani barsaya taakay tum ko is se ( Nehla kar ) pak kar day aur shaytani najasat ko tum se daur kardey. aur is liye bhi ke tumahray dilon ko mazboot kardey aur is se tumahray paon jamaye rakhay
  8,12,jab tumhara perwar-digaar firshton ko irshad farmata tha ke mein tumahray sath hon tum mominon ko tasalii do ke saabit qadam rahen. mein abhi abhi kafiroon ke dilon mein roab وہیبت daaley deta hon to un ke sir maar ( kar ) ura do aur un ka poor poor maar ( kar toar ) do
  8,13,yeh ( saza ) is liye di gayi ke unhon ne khuda aur is ke rasool ki mukhalfat ki. aur jo shakhs khuda aur is ke rasool ki mukhalfat karta hai to khuda bhi sakht azaab dainay wala hai
  8,14,yeh ( maza to yahan ) chako aur yeh ( jaane raho ) ke kafiroon ke liye ( akhirat mein ) dozakh ka azaab ( bhi tayyar ) hai
  8,15,ae ahal imaan jab maidan jung mein kufar se tmhar muqaabla ho to un se peeth nah pherna
  8,16,aur jo shakhs jung ke roz is soorat ke siwa ke larai ke liye kinare kinare chalay ( yani hikmat e amli se dushman ko maaray ) ya apni fouj mein ja milna chahay. un se peeth phairay ga to ( samjhoo ke ) woh khuda ke ghazab mein girftar hogaya aur is ka thikana dozakh hai. aur woh bohat hi buri jagah hai
  8,17,tum logon ne un ( kufar ) ko qatal nahikiya balkay khuda ne inhen qatalkiya. aur ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) jis waqt tum ne kankariyan pehnki theen to woh tum ne nahi pehnki theen balkay allah ne pehnki theen. is se yeh gharz thi ke mominon ko apne ( ehsaanon ) se achi terhan aazmaye. be shak khuda santa jaanta hai
  8,18,( baat ) yeh ( hai ) kuch shak nahi ke khuda kafiroon ki tadbeer ko kamzor kar dainay wala hai
  8,19,( kafroo ) agar tum ( Mohammad sale allah aleh wa-alehe wasallam par ) fatah chahtay ho to tumahray paas fatah aa chuki. ( dekho ) agar tum ( apne af-aal se ) baz aajao to tumahray haq mein behtar hai. aur agar phir ( nafarmani ) karo ge to hum bhi phir tumhe azaab karen ge aur tumhari jamaat khuwa kitni hi kaseer ho tumahray kuch bhi kaam nah aeye gi. aur khuda to mominon ke sath hai
  8,20,ae imaan walo! khuda aur is ke rasool ke hukum par chalo aur is se rogrdani nah karo aur tum suntay ho
  8,21,aur un logon jaisay nah hona jo kehte hain ke hum ne hukum ( khuda ) sun liya magar ( haqeeqat mein ) nahi suntay
  8,22,kuch shak nahi ke khuda ke nazdeek tamam jandaroon se badter behray gungay hain jo kuch nahi samajte
  8,23,aur agar khuda un mein neki ( ka madah ) daikhta to un ko suneney ki tofeq bakhshta. aur agar ( baghair salahiyat hadaayat ke ) samaat deta to woh munh phair kar bhaag jatay
  8,24,momino! khuda aur is ke rasool ka hukum qubool karo jab ke rasool khuda tumhe aisay kaam ke liye bulatay hain jo tum ko zindagi ( Jaudan ) bakhshta hai. aur jaan rakho ke khuda aadmi aur is ke dil ke darmain haamil hojata hai aur yeh bhi ke tum sab is ke rubaroo jama kiye jao ge
  8,25,aur is ftne se daro jo khasusiyat ke sath inhen logon par waqay nah hoga jo tum mein gunehgaar hain. aur jaan rakho ke khuda sakht azaab dainay wala hai
  8,26,aur is waqt ko yaad karo jab tum zameen ( mecca ) mein qaleel aur zaeef samjhay jatay they aur drtay rehtay they ke log tumhe urra ( nah ) le jayen ( yani be Khan-o-maan nah kar dein ) to is ne tum ko jagah di aur apni madad se tum ko taqwiyat bakhsh aur pakeeza cheezein khanay ko den taakay ( is ka ) shukar karo
  8,27,ae imaan walo! nah to khuda aur rasool ki amanat mein khayanat karo aur nah apni amanaton mein khayanat karo aur tum ( un baton ko ) jantay ho
  8,28,aur jaan rakho ke tumhara maal aur aulaad barri azmaish hai aur yeh ke khuda ke paas ( nakiyon ka ) bara sawab hai
  8,29,momino! agar tum khuda se daro ge to woh tumahray liye amar Faraq peda kardey ga ( yani tum ko mumtaz kardey ga ) to woh tumahray gunah mtade ga aur tumhe bakhash day ga. aur khuda bara fazl wala hai
  8,30,aur ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam is waqt ko yaad karo ) jab kafir log tumahray baray mein chaal chal rahay they ke tum ko qaid kar den ya jaan se maar dalain ya ( watan se ) nikaal den to ( idhar to ) woh chaal chal rahay they aur ( udhar ) khuda chaal chal raha tha. aur khuda sab se behtar chaal chalne wala hai
  8,31,aur jab un ko hamari ayatain parh kar sunai jati hain to kehte hain ( yeh kalaam ) hum ne sun liya hai agar hum chahain to isi terhan ka ( kalaam ) hum bhi keh den aur yeh hai hikiya sirf aglay logon ki hikaytein hain
  8,32,aur jab unhon ne kaha ke ae khuda agar yeh ( quran ) teri taraf se barhaq hai to hum par aasman se pathar barsa ya koi aur takleef dainay wala azaab bhaij
  8,33,aur khuda aisa nah tha ke jab taq tum un mein se they inhen azaab deta. aur aisa nah tha ke woh bakhshishen mangeen aur inhen azaab day
  8,34,aur ( ab ) un ke liye kon si wajah hai ke woh inhen azaab nah day jab ke woh masjid mohtaram ( mein namaz parhnay ) se roktay hain aur woh is masjid ke matwalli bhi nahi. is ke matwalli to sirf parhaizgaar hain. lekin un mein aksar nahi jantay
  8,35,aur un logon ki namaz Khana kaaba ke paas seetiyan aur taliyan bajanay ke siwa kuch nah thi. to tum jo kufar karte they ab is ke badlay azaab ( ka maza ) chako
  8,36,jo log kafir hain apna maal kharch karte hain ke ( logon ko ) khuda ke raste se rokain. so abhi aur kharch karen ge magar aakhir woh ( kharch karna ) un ke liye ( mojab ) afsos hoga aur woh maghloob ho jaien ge. aur kafir log dozakh ki taraf hankay jayen ge
  8,37,taakay khuda napak ko pak se allag kar day aur napak ko aik dosray par rakh kar aik dhair bana day. phir is ko dozakh mein daal day. yahi log khasara panay walay hain
  8,38,( ae paighambar ) kufar se keh do ke agar woh apne af-aal se baz ajayeen to jo hochuka woh inhen maaf kardiya jaye ga. aur agar phir ( wohi harkaat ) karne lagen ge to aglay logon ka ( jo ) tareeq jari hochuka hai ( wohi un ke haq mein brta jaye ga )
  8,39,aur un logon se lartay raho yahan taq ke fitnah ( yani kufar ka fasaad ) baqi nah rahay aur deen sab khuda hi ka hojaye aur agar baz ajayeen to khuda un ke kamon ko dekh raha hai
  8,40,aur agar rogrdani karen to jaan rakho ke khuda tumhara himayati hai. ( aur ) woh khoob himayati aur khoob madadgaar hai
  8,41,aur jaan rakho ke jo cheez tum ( kufar se ) lout kar lao is mein se panchawan hissa khuda ka aur is ke rasool ka aur ahal qaraabat ka aur yatimon ka aur mohtajon ka aur musafiron ka hai. agar tum khuda par aur is ( nusrat ) par imaan rakhtay ho jo ( haq o batil mein ) farq karne ke din ( yani jung badar mein ) jis din dono foujon mein mudh bheer hogayi. apne bande ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) par nazil farmai. aur khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  8,42,jis waqt tum ( madeeney se ) qareeb ke nakay par they aur kafir baeed ke nakay par aur qaafla tum se neechay ( utar gaya ) tha. aur agar tum ( jung ke liye ) aapas mein qarardad kar lete to waqt Moueen ( par jama honay ) mein taqdeem o takheer ho jati. lekin khuda ko Manzoor tha ke jo kaam ho kar rehne wala tha usay kar hi daaley taakay jo marey baseerat par ( yani yaqeen jaan kar ) marey aur jo jeeta rahay woh bhi baseerat par ( yani haq pehchan kar ) jeeta rahay. aur kuch shak nahi ke khuda santa jaanta hai
  8,43,is waqt khuda ne tumhe khawab mein kafiroon ko thori tadaad mein dekhaya. aur agar bohat kar ke dekhata to tum log jee chore dete aur ( jo ) kaam ( darpaish tha is ) mein jhagrnay lagtay lekin khuda ne ( tumhe is se ) bacha liya. be shak woh seenon ki baton taq se waaqif hai
  8,44,aur is waqt jab tum aik dosray ke maqabil hue to kafiroon ko tumhari nazron mein thora kar ke dekhata tha aur tum ko un ki nigahon mein thora kar ke dekhata tha taakay khuda ko jo kaam Manzoor karna tha usay kar daaley. aur sab kamon ka rujoo khuda ki taraf hai
  8,45,momino! jab ( kufar ki ) kisi jamaat se tumhara muqaabla ho to saabit qadam raho aur khuda ko bohat yaad karo taakay morad haasil karo
  8,46,aur khuda aur is ke rasool ke hukum par chalo aur aapas mein jhagra nah karna ke ( aisa karo ge to ) tum buzdil ho jao ge aur tumhara Iqbal jata rahay ga aur sabr se kaam lau. ke khuda sabr karne walon ka madadgaar hai
  8,47,aur un logon jaisay nah hona jo itratay hue ( yani haq ka muqaabla karne ke liye ) aur logon ko dikhaane ke liye gharon se nikal aeye aur logon ko khuda ki raah se roktay hain. aur jo aamaal yeh karte hain khuda un par ihata kiye hue hai
  8,48,aur jab shaitano ne un ke aamaal un ko aaraasta kar ke dukhaay aur kaha ke aaj ke din logon mein koi tum par ghalib nah hoga aur mein tumhara Rafeeq hon ( lekin ) jab dono faujein aik dosray ke maqabil saf aaraa huien to paspaa ho kar chal diya aur kehnay laga ke mujhe tum se koi vaastaa nahi. mein to aisi cheezein dekh raha hon jo tum nahi dekh satke. mujhe to khuda se dar lagta hai. aur khuda sakht azaab karne wala hai
  8,49,is waqt munhafiq aur ( kafir ) jin ke dilon mein marz tha kehte they ke un logon ko un ke deen ne maghrour kar rakha hai aur jo shakhs khuda par bharosa rakhta hai to khuda ghalib hikmat wala hai
  8,50,aur kash tum is waqt ( ki kefiyat ) dekho. jab farishtay kafiroon ki jaanen nikaltay hain un ke monhon aur pithon par ( korray aur hathoray waghera ) maartay ( hain aur kehte hain ) ke ( ab ) azaab aatish ( ka maza ) chako
  8,51,yeh un ( aamaal ) ki saza hai jo tumahray hathon ne agay beje hain. aur yeh ( jaan rakho ) ke khuda bundon par zulm nahi karta
  8,52,jaissa haal fironiyon aur un se pehlay logon ka ( howa tha waisa hi un ka howa ke ) unhon ne khuda ki ayaton se kufarkiya to khuda ne un ke gunaaho ki saza mein un ko pakar liya. be shak khuda zabardast aur sakht azaab dainay wala hai
  8,53,yeh is liye ke jo Nemat khuda kisi qoum ko diya karta hai jab taq woh khud apne dilon ki haalat nah badal dalain khuda usay nahi badla karta. aur is liye ke khuda santa jaanta hai
  8,54,jaissa haal firounion aur un se pehlay logon ka ( howa tha waisa hi un ka howa ) unhon ne apne perwar-digaar ki ayaton ko jhatlaya to hum ne un ko un ke gunaaho ke sabab halaak kar dala aur firounion ko duubo diya. aur woh sab zalim they
  8,55,jandaroon mein sab se badter khuda ke nazdeek woh log hain jo kafir hain so woh imaan nahi laatay
  8,56,jin logon se tum ne ( sulah ka ) ehadkiya hai phir woh har baar apne ehad ko toar daaltay hain aur ( khuda se ) nahi drtay
  8,57,agar tum un ko larai mein pao to inhen aisi saza do ke jo log un ke pas pusht hain woh un ko dekh kar bhaag jayen ajab nahi ke un ko ( is se ) Ibrat ho
  8,58,aur agar tum ko kisi qoum se dagha baazi ka khauf ho to ( un ka ehad ) inhen ki taraf pheink do ( aur ) barabar ( ka jawab do ) kuch shak nahi ke khuda daghabazon ko dost nahi rakhta
  8,59,aur kafir yeh nah khayaal karen ke woh bhaag niklay hain. woh ( apni chalon se hum ko ) hargiz aajiz nahi kar saktay
  8,60,aur jahan taq hosakay ( fouj ki jamiat ke ) zor se aur ghoron ke tayyar rakhnay se un ke ( muqablay ke ) liye mustaed raho ke is se khuda ke dushmanon aur tumahray dushmanon aur un ke siwa aur logon par jin ko tum nahi jantay aur khuda jaanta hai Haibat baithi rahay gi. aur tum jo kuch raah khuda mein kharch karo ge is ka sawab tum ko poora poora diya jaye ga aur tumhara zara nuqsaan nahikiya jaye ga
  8,61,aur agar yeh log sulah ki taraf mael hon to tum bhi is ki taraf mael ho jao aur khuda par bharosa rakho. kuch shak nahi ke woh sab kuch santa ( aur ) jaanta hai
  8,62,aur agar yeh chahain ke tum ko fraib den to khuda tumhe kifayat kere ga. wohi to hai jis ne tum ko apni madad se aur musalmanoon ( ki jamiat ) se taqwiyat bakhsh
  8,63,aur un ke dilon mein ulfat peda kar di. aur agar tum duniya bhar ki doulat kharch karte tab bhi un ke dilon mein ulfat nah peda kar saktay. magar khuda hi ne un mein ulfat daal di. be shak woh zabardast ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  8,64,ae nabi! khuda tum ko aur mominon ko jo tumahray pairo hain kaafi hai
  8,65,ae nabi! musalmanoon ko jehaad ki targheeb do. aur agar tum bees aadmi saabit qadam rehne walay hon ge to do so kafiroon par ghalib rahen ge. aur agar so ( aisay ) hon ge to hazaar par ghalib rahen ge. is liye ke kafir aisay log hain ke kuch bhi samajh nahi rakhtay
  8,66,ab khuda ne tum par se boojh halka kar diya aur maloom karliya ke ( abhi ) tum mein kisi qader kamzoree hai. pas agar tum mein aik so saabit qadam rehne walay hon ge to do so par ghalib rahen ge. aur agar aik hazaar hon ge to khuda ke hukum se do hazaar par ghalib rahen ge. aur khuda saabit qadam rehne walon ka madad gaar hai
  8,67,paighambar ko Shayan nahi ke is ke qabzay mein qaidi rahen jab taq ( kafiroon ko qatal kar ke ) zameen mein kasrat se khoon ( nah ) baha day. tum log duniya ke maal ke taalib ho. aur khuda akhirat ( ki bhalai ) chahta hai. aur khuda ghalib hikmat wala hai
  8,68,agar khuda ka hukum pehlay nah hochuka hota to jo ( Fidya ) tum ne liya hai is ke badlay tum par bara azaab nazil hota
  8,69,to jo mal-e ghanemat tumhe mila hai usay khao ( ke woh tumahray liye ) halal Tayyab rahay aur khuda se drtay raho. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  8,70,ae paighambar jo qaidi tumahray haath mein ( girftar ) hain un se keh do ke agar khuda tumahray dilon mein neki maloom kere ga to jo ( maal ) tum se chhin gaya hai is se behtar tumhe inayat farmaiye ga aur tumahray gunah bhi maaf kar day ga aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  8,71,aur agar yeh log tum se dagha karna chahain ge to yeh pehlay hi khuda se dagha kar chukay hain to is ne un ko ( tumahray ) qabzay mein kar diya. aur khuda Dana hikmat wala hai
  8,72,jo log imaan laaye aur watan se hijrat kar gay aur khuda ki raah mein apne maal aur jaan se larray woh aur jinhon ne ( hijrat karne walon ko ) jagah di aur un ki madad ki woh aapas mein aik dosray ke Rafeeq hain. aur jo log imaan to le aeye lekin hijrat nahi ki to jab taq woh hijrat nah karen tum ko un ki rafaqat se kuch sarokaar nahi. aur agar woh tum se deen ( ke mamlaat ) mein madad talab karen to tum ko madad karni lazim hogi. magar un logon ke muqablay mein ke tum mein aur un mein ( sulah ka ) ehad ho ( madad nahi karni chahiye ) aur khuda tumahray sab kamon ko dekh raha hai
  8,73,aur jo log kafir hain ( woh bhi ) aik dosray ke Rafeeq hain. to ( momino ) agar tum yeh ( kaam ) nah karo ge to malik mein fitnah barpaa ho jaye ga aur bara fasaad mache ga
  8,74,aur jo log imaan laaye aur watan se hijrat kar gay aur khuda ki raah mein laraiyan karte rahay aur jinhon ne ( hijrat karne walon ko ) jagah di aur un ki madad ki. yahi log sachey musalman hain. un ke liye ( khuda ke haan ) bakhshish aur izzat ki rozi hai
  8,75,aur jo log baad mein imaan laaye aur watan se hijrat kargaye aur tumahray sath ho kar jehaad karte rahay woh bhi tum hi mein se hain. aur rishta daar khuda ke hukum ki ro se aik dosray ke ziyada haqdaar hain. kuch shak nahi ke khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
